      <title>莫迪指控安巴尼和阿达尼向反对党提供非法现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/modi-alleges-ambani-adani-giving-opposition-party-illegal-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪表示，主要反对党从亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼和高塔姆·阿达尼那里收受非法现金，以资助其竞选活动，这一令人惊讶的指控发生在一场激烈的投票战中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/modi-alleges-ambani-adani-giving-opposition-party-illegal-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国商业游说团体加入降息呼吁，下调 GDP 预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/thai-business-lobby-joins-rate-cut-call-as-it-trims-gdp-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最大的商业游说团体在大幅下调自己对经济增长的预期后，敦促央行降息，并与政府合作寻找重振商业和消费活动的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/thai-business-lobby-joins-rate-cut-call-as-it-trims-gdp-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国核监督机构在关键报告发布前对伊朗发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/un-nuclear-watchdog-puts-iran-on-notice-ahead-of-key-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗只有几周的时间来遵守联合国核监督机构发出的监测要求，否则将面临新一轮外交谴责的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/un-nuclear-watchdog-puts-iran-on-notice-ahead-of-key-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 07:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港政府赢得禁止流行抗议歌曲的上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hong-kong-court-approves-government-ban-of-protest-song</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港法院允许政府禁止一首带有犯罪意图的流行抗议歌曲，此举可能会引发人们对该市言论自由受到削弱的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hong-kong-court-approves-government-ban-of-protest-song</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 07:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国银行、内格尔在欧盟投票前呼吁反对仇外心理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-banks-nagel-make-call-against-xenophobia-before-eu-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国银行家计划在下个月欧洲议会选举之前签署一封反对仇外心理的公开信，这是由德国央行和游说团体法兰克福金融集团发起的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-banks-nagel-make-call-against-xenophobia-before-eu-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 06:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国当局在最新一次针对政客的袭击后保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-authorities-on-alert-after-latest-attack-on-politician</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国当局正在调查柏林国务部长和前市长遭到身份不明的袭击者袭击的事件，这是下个月欧洲议会选举前政治暴力激增的最新证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-authorities-on-alert-after-latest-attack-on-politician</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
